title: Khatarnak Khiladi
subTitle: Maduravel, a humble vegetable vendor, protects an elderly woman and her two daughters. However, an altercation with local thugs unexpectedly reveals his true identity.

title: Saptagiri Express
subTitle: A happy-go-lucky actor is forced to do his father's job after his unexpected demise. However, when he realises his father was murdered, he sets out to exact vengeance.

title: Marzi The Power
subTitle: Krishnaveni runs away from home to elope with her lover, Kishore, who does not show up. Gani, a self-centred man, plans to take her to her father, hoping to make a quick buck.

title: Filler
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Mr Joe B. Carvalho
subTitle: A private detective is tasked by a businessman to find his daughter. However, while investigating, he gets involved with his former girlfriend, a policewoman who is chasing an international criminal.

title: Triple R Rocky Rahul Rambo
subTitle: Three students, who fail their exams and waste their time, befriend a girl in their college. They devise a plan to help her, but it leads to various problems.

title: Kabzaa - The Mafia Raaj
subTitle: Vijay Chandra, a determined police aspirant, battles a local MLA's corrupt efforts to seize his family's land. Joined by other wronged citizens, he takes a stand for justice and honor.

title: Jaanbaz Ki Jung
subTitle: An idle young man falls for a doctor who saved his mother. However, she asks him to kill a drug lord for her love, revealing her hidden revenge plot for her murdered family.

title: Fidaa
subTitle: An NRI medical student falls in love with a vivacious woman. However, they face challenges in their relationship due to their differences in personalities.

title: Chhaava
subTitle: Following the death of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj, his son, the Maratha king Sambhaji, takes a stand against the brutal Mughal emperor, Aurangzeb, in a bid to protect his empire.

title: DNA
subTitle: Due to their precarious mental health, Divya and Anand's marriage faces numerous challenges that test their relationship.

title: Diesel
subTitle: A driven and determined young man is forced to confront ruthless and corrupt authorities after becoming ensnared in the dangerous web of the diesel mafia.

title: Khaidi No. 150
subTitle: Seenu, a criminal, escapes from the prison and places his doppelganger, Shankar, in his place. However, upon learning about Shankar's noble mission, he takes up the cause himself.

title: Khaidi No. 150
subTitle: Seenu, a criminal, escapes from the prison and places his doppelganger, Shankar, in his place. However, upon learning about Shankar's noble mission, he takes up the cause himself.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Rudra Suryavanshi
subTitle: Gunasingam, a rich farmer, lives a humble life with his family. However, things take a turn when he falls in love with the most beautiful woman in the village.

title: Mickey Virus
subTitle: When the woman he loves regrets a web transaction, a hacker decides to help her undo it. However, chaos ensues when he accidentally commits a robbery instead.

title: Angrezi Mein Kehte Hain
subTitle: Yashwant, a middle-aged man, refrains from expressing his love for his wife, Kiran. As a result, their relationship develops cracks, and they decide to part ways.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jihadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Roberrt
subTitle: Raghava, the head cook in a catering unit, leads a peaceful life with his son Arjun. However, their bliss is short-lived as Raghava's past comes back to haunt him.

title: Baaghi 2
subTitle: Ronny, a soldier, learns of the disappearance of the daughter of his former lover. Soon, his intense investigation leads him to uncover a web of crimes and a secret from the past.

title: Devaki Nandana Vasudeva
subTitle: When a prophecy declares that his nephew will cause his downfall, Kamsaraja becomes worried and stops at nothing to take him down.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi
subTitle: A man and a woman develop a great bond after the latter arrives in Hyderabad. However, they realise their love for each other when the woman's marriage is arranged to a person of her parent's choice.

title: Dashing CM Bharath
subTitle: Oxford graduate Bharat assumes his late father's role as chief minister. He strives to reform a corrupt society, but encounters fierce opposition from adversaries.

title: Shootout at Lokhandwala
subTitle: A notorious gangster rules over the Mumbai's underworld with an iron fist. However, his growing influence prompts a group of police officers to plot a strategy to clear the city of organised crime.

title: Shootout at Lokhandwala
subTitle: A notorious gangster rules over the Mumbai's underworld with an iron fist. However, his growing influence prompts a group of police officers to plot a strategy to clear the city of organised crime.

title: Mahadev Ka Gorakhpur
subTitle: When evil descends chaotically upon the goodness of the land, a righteous warrior of Lord Shiva arrives to deliver justice to the wicked.

title: Wagah
subTitle: An Indian soldier falls in love with a Muslim girl near the India-Pakistan border. However, when a riot breaks out in the area, the man finds his love and his life at risk.

title: One Way Ticket
subTitle: Kunjappu, a jeep driver and an ardent admirer of superstar Mammootty, finds himself troubled when his relationship is in disarray. But he is rapt when Mammootty himself intervenes to solve his issues.

title: I Proud to Be an Indian
subTitle: I, a man from India, travels to London for a family wedding and finds that their community is being threatened by a racist group. Seeing this, he decides to get involved and fight back.

title: Thadam
subTitle: While investigating the death of a man, the police track down their lead suspect. However, the case takes a twisted turn when they discover a clone of their suspect.

title: Theeran Adhigaaram Ondru
subTitle: Theeran, a dedicated police officer, pays the price for his honesty and faces hardships when he tries to investigate the illegal activities conducted by a powerful gangster.

title: Rider
subTitle: As love blossoms between orphans Chinnu and Kitty, fate separates them as children. However, they grow up yearning to find each other.

title: Maragadha Naanayam
subTitle: Senguttuvan and Elango work for a smuggler who hires them to retrieve an emerald medallion, a cursed treasure linked to many deaths. Seeking help, they consult a priest and summon three spirits to locate it.

title: Tanhaji: The Unsung Warrior
subTitle: Tanhaji, a Maratha warrior, is Shivaji Maharaj's trusted lieutenant. When the Mughals invade and conquer Kondhana fort, he sets out to reclaim it for his king and country.

title: ACP Shiva
subTitle: Shivakumar IPS, a corrupt police officer, joins GK, a local politician, in his immoral activities. However, when GK's brother kills his best friend, he decides to turn over a new leaf.

title: Chithha
subTitle: Living a quiet life with his niece, Eeswaran manages to provide for her and nurtures her like a parent. However, his journey takes an insidous turn when she goes missing.
